    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/9f934b02a9047dd8fbcf4a45ef0014ac.poster.avif?t=1740582229\" width=640 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/9f934b02a9047dd8fbcf4a45ef0014ac.webm?t=1740582229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>传说中存在着万界门，这是一个通往无数空间世界的神奇门户。这些世界各不相同，有的充满了美丽与神秘，有的则危险重重，有的拥有无尽的财富，有的蕴含着强大的能量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/7b8784eed2a6ec4faa821c1cb53e12f6.avif?t=1740582229\" width=640 height=247 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/20a6f6ee8fb2443906ad1edf54ce62f6.avif?t=1740582229\" width=500 height=156 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过传送门生成器生成传送门，可以打造独属于自己的商店。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过传送门道具礼包丰富商店传送门卡池，打造自己独属自己的商店卡池。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/0c8726173d8e17570c22debbb75292f8.poster.avif?t=1740582229\" width=500 height=331 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/0c8726173d8e17570c22debbb75292f8.webm?t=1740582229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/89e83d0e89da92458729f6a8843625d3.avif?t=1740582229\" width=500 height=156 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁金币上限锁，积累巨量财富。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刷新商店很畅快不过要注意，每次刷新都会使刷新所需金币翻倍哦！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/4b7c28a5765478e77b4e01cad1d20c13.poster.avif?t=1740582229\" width=500 height=311 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/4b7c28a5765478e77b4e01cad1d20c13.webm?t=1740582229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/8eb4e740de92aba0c512771076c37cd2.avif?t=1740582229\" width=500 height=156 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背包与系统界面完全融合，新颖的空间布局。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两边的指示圈每次转动都代表世界的切换。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意在战场世界时间一直在流逝！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/fffd32d25eeded720b2db89331aded27.poster.avif?t=1740582229\" width=500 height=311 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/fffd32d25eeded720b2db89331aded27.webm?t=1740582229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/90caaa22d93c25ecff9717b7e00bfbe0.avif?t=1740582229\" width=500 height=156 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意敌人会随着世界等级的提升越来越强大！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/d98f5f576e0dfecacec7a01058d00538.poster.avif?t=1740582229\" width=500 height=331 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/d98f5f576e0dfecacec7a01058d00538.webm?t=1740582229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/e7ce2357d2c8cd472f6058cc5b0a6ed1.poster.avif?t=1740582229\" width=640 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157870/extras/e7ce2357d2c8cd472f6058cc5b0a6ed1.webm?t=1740582229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
